{"tid":976453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法醫稱每年百人自慰致死　最常見的是「窒息」","createTime":"2019-01-10T11:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T12:58:55.000Z","uid":121473,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"51e7df0e7ac2345d835b32261fc21fb1c9bea4d9","tid":976453,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:53:36.000Z","msg":"德國布蘭登堡一位法醫指出，高風險的自慰是難以預料且危險的殺手，每年全國有近百人死於自慰。<br />\n<br />\n據《BBC中文網》報導，沃斯（Harald Voss）指出，死於高風險自慰的人，多是因為普通自慰不能讓他們滿足，所以尋求更刺激的自慰方式，而致死最多的原因是窒息，其他常見的死因是電擊。沃斯也曾提到他遇到的離奇死亡案件，像是有男子在身上覆蓋了乳酪片，上身套上褲襪，再穿上雨衣和潛水服，然後用塑膠袋套頭坐在暖器前，最後身亡。<br />\n<br />\n沃斯也提到另一個案例，一位母親發現自己兒子的遺體時，兒子的乳頭上夾著聖誕樹的燈炮，死因是觸電。沃斯說，高風險自慰者遍佈各年齡段，但大部分受害者是男性，因為女性在自我情欲體驗中往往更謹慎。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190110/1498473/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190110%2F1498473%2F&d=ap59pJTNiO3%2Foi%2FwQdieBywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=0f377215\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190110%2F1498473%2F&h=354183d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190110/1498473/</a><br />\n<br />\n各位是時候戒丁了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da9b0b506090ce64e075524d2ad5285ed5c9d84","tid":976453,"uid":65774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"欣怡既窒息性愛岩哂呢班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44eba6794572dd2d01d944cde9474bbb3317683b","tid":976453,"uid":121473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7da9b0b506090ce64e075524d2ad5285ed5c9d84","tid":976453,"uid":65774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"欣怡既窒息性愛岩哂呢班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8579362aae5226bca326b561f8e2aa6e19283dbc","tid":976453,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"像是有男子在身上覆蓋了乳酪片，上身套上褲襪，再穿上雨衣和潛水服，然後用塑膠袋套頭坐在暖器前，最後身亡。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6e9af1d80608fda91ccd01dd056e6448c82810","tid":976453,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:50:00.000Z","msg":"打十幾年丁真係打到無哂feel, 行禮如儀交功課咁, 又難怪佢地既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9be27412533ca274eba803339896c9f8a56abbd","tid":976453,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/05/6e/e6/056ee6ace2fc6664cc6dbdaa74026b19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F05%2F6e%2Fe6%2F056ee6ace2fc6664cc6dbdaa74026b19.jpg&h=c233d196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDavid Carradine<br />\nKill Bill個Bill <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.cdn.turner.com/ireport/sm/prod/2009/06/06/WE00266168/519652/Anon1244267631-BangkokNewspaperPublishesDavidCarrad877087_lg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.cdn.turner.com%2Fireport%2Fsm%2Fprod%2F2009%2F06%2F06%2FWE00266168%2F519652%2FAnon1244267631-BangkokNewspaperPublishesDavidCarrad877087_lg.jpg&h=af4021f4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}